{"tid":1353311,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非入] 如果決定咗27號入元朗，你地跟唔跟?","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:31.000Z","uid":190579,"like":45,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d02dc944c4fbed5091aaa4b30863fd014e171cdc","tid":1353311,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"認真，如果唔夠人，警犬同鄉黑係絕對可以包抄勇武派，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一舉坑殺我方所有精銳</span></span><br />\n不要濫情，叫和理非唔好出，元朗留番勇武解決既人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係陷勇武於死地</span></span><br />\n當年二戰德軍勢如破竹，真正負責包抄圍剿打爆法國既其實得嗰幾個坦甲師。但如果冇後面幾十個步兵師支援，得嗰幾個坦甲師衝，好快比人反包圍一舉殲滅。我召喚各位和理非出嚟，做勇武坦克車身後既步兵師<br />\n<br />\n特殊例外<br />\n1) 負戰力唔好跟 e.g. 大肚婆<br />\n2) 唔好帶小朋友<br />\nps 唔齊裝既人唔係例外，呢兩日去買齊佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔跟"},{"pid":"9d2bc2a8faad9979da15977fb1b321b7c2563168","tid":1353311,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a9ebcf972cbde33c5b722815cd5f090f21b2e10","tid":1353311,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e12ddbc2500775ff3baf309deeb7d35dedb9c78","tid":1353311,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccf637d65b91b71a0841b6362a3faf569bcb6fa3","tid":1353311,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3a2dd28de152d8abe25dafc1aa4379ab1026565","tid":1353311,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"跟細良講, 跟, 但唔用裝備<br />\n任何一個兄弟少條毛<br />\n你鄧偉強都唔撚掂"},{"pid":"2563a98a8d2b53b3474b74cc656bcb716eb4759b","tid":1353311,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-2